question: Which fast food restaurant is on the path towards Cosmetic Surgeons of Michigan, PC, St. Clair Shores, MI within a 60 kilometers radius from Sea Life Aquarium, Auburn Hills, MI?
sql:
WITH
    angle AS (SELECT degrees(ST_Azimuth(ST_GeomFromText('POINT (-83.296505 42.70361)',4326)::geography, ST_GeomFromText('POINT (-82.900778 42.460402)',4326)::geography)) AS value)
SELECT * FROM pois,angle
WHERE amenity = 'fast_food'
AND ST_DWithin(pois.geometry, ST_GeomFromText('POINT (-83.296505 42.70361)',4326)::geography, 60000)
AND (degrees(ST_Azimuth(ST_GeomFromText('POINT (-83.296505 42.70361)',4326)::geography, pois.geometry)) BETWEEN angle.value - 22.5 AND angle.value + 22.5);

[3].display_name: Sea Life Aquarium, Auburn Hills, MI

[4].display_name: Cosmetic Surgeons of Michigan, PC, St. Clair Shores, MI
